        <item>
            <title>九号电动误将 M95c+ 价格标成 500 元，拍下的用户首台车辆可正常提车</title>
            <description>&lt;div class=&quot;tougao-user&quot;&gt;感谢 IT 之家网友 &lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D228157&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;爱丫爱丫&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D792075&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;大逆转之炜&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1516578&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;YMM&lt;/a&gt; 的线索投递！&lt;/div&gt;
